quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Usikelelekile loWo eSandleni saKhe kukho uBukumkani, Onamandla ngaphezulu kwezinto zonke"
  67,2,"Yena loWo Wadala ukufa nokuphila ukuze Anivavanye (kucace ukuba) nguwuphi na kuni olungileyo ngezenzo. Yena nguSobunganga, uMxoleli"
  67,3,"Yena lowo Wadala amazulu asixhenxe alekeneyo. Akuboni kungangqinelani endalweni kaSozinceba. Ngoko ke guquka ujonge (esibhakabhakeni), likhona na ithanda olibonayo"
  67,4,Phinda ujonge kwakhona okwesibini. (Oko) kujonga (kwakho) kuya kubuyela kuwe kuthobekile kudiniwe
  67,5,"Inene Sihombise izulu elikufuphi ngezibane (iinkwenkwezi), Senza kananjalo ngazo oko kugityiselwa ngako amashayâtîn (ooSathana), yaye Sibalungiselele isohlwayo seDangatya"
  67,6,"Ke kaloku okwabo bangakholwayo eNkosini yabo sisohlwayo sesiHogo, hayi ukuba libi kwekhaya (labo) lokugqibela"
  67,7,"Xa bejulwa kuso, beva ukubizela kwaso (okoyikisayo) lo gama sibila nokubila"
  67,8,"Siphantsela ukugqabhuka ngumsindo, maxa onke iqela (elithile) liphoswa ngaphakathi kuso, abagcini baso bayababuza: “Akuzanga kufike Mlumkisi na kuni?”"
  67,9,"(Baphendula) bathi bona: “Ewe, uMlumkisi wayefikile kuthi kodwasamphikisathinasathi:“UAllâhakukhontoAyithumele phantsi, nina (baLumkisi) aninto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba sekulahlekeni okukhulu.”"
  67,10,"Kananjalo baya kuthi: “Akwaba sasiphulaphule okanye saqiqa, ngesingabangakho phakathi kwamadlelane eDangatya loMlilo"
  67,11,"Ke kaloku baya kusivuma isono sabo, ngoko ke kude lee ngabahlali baseDangatyeni loMlilo"
  67,12,"Inene abo bayoyikayo iNkosi yabo Engabonwayo, okwabo iya kuba kukuxolelwa nomvuzo omkhulu"
  67,13,"Ke kaloku nokuba ningazifihla iintetho zenu zasekhusini okanye niziveze elubala, Yena nguMazi woko kusezifubeni (zabantu)"
  67,14,"Akamelanga kwazi na loWo Wadalayo? Kananjalo Yena nguSobubele, Onolwazi (lweento zonke)"
  67,15,NguYe Owenza umhlaba waba phantsi kolawulo lwenu ngoko ke hambani phakathi kwamathambeka wawo nidle kwimbonelelo yaKhe ukanti kukuYe apho uvuko lukhoyo
  67,16,"Ingaba niziva nikhuselekile na ukuba Yena loWo Usezulwini Akanakuwenza umhlaba uniginye, uthi kananjalo ngokukhawuleza ujikeleze (nani)?”"
  67,17,Okanye niziva nikhuselekile ekubeni loWo Usezulwini Akanakuthumela isiphango samatye ngokuchasene nani na? Niya kwazi ke okokuba saba (sibi) kanjani na isilumkiso saM
  67,18,Kananjalo sele baphika kakade abo bangaphambili kunabo saba njani ke isiyalo saM
  67,19,"Abaziboni\tna\tiintaka\t(eziphaphazela)\tphezu\tkwabo ngamaphiko avuliweyo (ngaxa limbi) evalekile? Akukho bani uzibambayo (ukuba zibe sesibhakabhakeni) ngaphandle koSozinceba. Inene Yena nguSokubona ngaphezu kweento zonke"
  67,20,Kanti ngubani na onokuba ngumkhosi wenu anincede ngaphandle koSozinceba? Abangakholwayo abakho ntweni ngaphandle kwenkohliso
  67,21,Ingubani khona onokunondla ukuba Ebenokusuka Ayibambe imbonelelo yaKhe (kuni)? Kodwa bona bathe gqolo ngokudelela nokuchasa (inkolo)
  67,22,Ingaba lowo uhamba erhubuluza ngobuso bakhe ukhokeleleke ngcono na kunalowo umi nkqo eNdleleni ethe Tye
  67,23,"Yithi: “NguYe Onivelisileyo, Waninika ukuva nokubona neentliziyo, kuncinane eninombulelo ngako.”"
  67,24,"Yithi: “NguYe Onenze naba baninzi ngokuphindeneyo emhlabeni, yaye kukuYe apho niza kuqokelelwa khona.”"
  67,25,"Ke kaloku bathi: “Sinini na esisi thembiso, ukuba (nina bakholwayo) nithetha inyaniso?”"
  67,26,"Yithi: “Ulwazi (loko) lukuAllâh, mna ndinguMlumkisi ocacileyo.”"
  67,27,"Kodwa ukusibona kwabo sisondela, ubuso babo bangakholwayo, buya kunxunguphala kuze kuthiwe (kubo): “Oko ke koko nanikubiza"
  67,28,"Yithi (Muhammad), “Niyabona phofu ukuba uAllâh Anganditshabalalisa ndawonye nabo bakunye nam okanye Asenzele inceba, ngubani ongabakhusela bona abangakholwayo esohlwayeni esibuhlungu"
  67,29,"Yithi: “NguSolubabalo; thina sikholiwe kuYe, kananjalo kukuYe apho sixhomekeke khona. Kwaye niza kwazi okokuba ngubani na osekulahlekeni okucacileyo.”"
  67,30,"Yithi: “Niyijongile phofu (yona into yokuba): xa amanzi wenu ebenokusuka atshoniswe emhlabeni, ngubani omnye obeza kunizela namanzi ampompozayo"